  <description>
    <p>Quake 4 is the true sequel to Quake II, continuing the Strogg vs. Humans storyline
        from the point where Quake II ended.</p>
    <p>This is a Flatpak distribution of the official Linux port of the game, for
        ease of use as the game can be difficult to run on modern systems.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include the Quake 4 game data or a CD key. You will need
        to supply both. At least the files <code>pak001.pk4</code> through <code>pak012.pk4</code>
        from a retail installation of Quake 4 must be copied to
        <code>$HOME/.var/app/io.github.glkarin.quake4/q4base/</code>.</p>
  </description>
